Download Rust through "rustup" which is a command line tool for managing all the Rust versions and its associated tools.

Link: https://www.rust-lang.org/install.html 


$ rustc --version   
rustc 1.44.1 (c7087fe00 2020-06-17)
$ 

Updating & Uninstalling
$ rustup update  
info: no updatable toolchains installed
info: checking for self-updates
info: downloading self-update

Uninstall 
$ rustup self uninstall  